      <abstract>
        <p>Liquidation of the ghetto at Wieliczka (Aug. 1942). Transports to the forced labour camp
          in Stalowa Wola. Individual and mass executions. Author’s escape with the group of 85
          prisoners (July 1944)</p>
      </abstract>
